{"tid":84217,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"走過落魄困境 車保羅笑談娛圈人無情","createTime":"2017-01-17T11:18:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T10:00:19.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b86e74ca22da92ac7b80e8c9f56115625bb6ff88","tid":84217,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:18:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170116/280pix/1484541480_db59.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170116%2F280pix%2F1484541480_db59.jpg&h=4179bf36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170117&amp;guid=56179453&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170117%26guid%3D56179453%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&d=sEtQ1DUxG56JTG4DW6ZSv6EBD16zEvtm8%2BkmVdQ%2BVC0%3D&h=3dd967bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170117%26guid%3D56179453%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&h=db054207\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170117&amp;guid=56179453&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n八九十年代是香港娛樂圈電影圈最蓬勃的時期，亦是車保羅(Paul)出道以至成名的日子，拍過《第一類型危險》、《香港也瘋狂》、《審死官》等作品。那時候這位外型獨特的綠葉戲接戲，廣告接廣告，風光得意；而03年約滿無線後卻跌落谷底，走投無路要領取綜援，外孫女亦發生交通意外，坎坷失意。試過高低起跌嚐盡人生百味，阿Paul仍然覺得自己很僥倖，「可以做回一個人」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170116/280pix/1484541396_9a3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170116%2F280pix%2F1484541396_9a3c.jpg&h=08733323&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb8286b788aa962c5c77ff17e229b5c366aaf734","tid":84217,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:19:56.000Z","msg":"「嗰時啱啱同無綫約滿，佢哋就話換另一方式續約，一年二千蚊底薪，我咪算數，寧願走出去啦。」加入失業大軍的Paul， 嘗試應徵不同類型的工種，卻因演員身份而不獲聘用，「一句大明星喎請你唔起，咁就冇啦。」所以他就領取了數個月綜援，後來朋友知道他如斯境況，就介紹他工作。曾經遠走他鄉打工，亦試過做保安、地盤雜工等勞動工種，阿Paul說雖辛苦兼收入不穩定，但總好過坐在家中等運到。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170116/280pix/1484541395_303a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170116%2F280pix%2F1484541395_303a.jpg&h=43e5ed62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n結婚超過廿五年，太太一直陪他走過高山低谷的日子，所以夢想就是送老婆一粒鑽石<br />\n<br />\n要走過這段落魄的日子其實一點也不容易，還是承受真真實實的人情冷暖。「最現實嘅係有一個副導演，我結婚時佢又出車出人，乜都入佢數。但到我出現咗問題想借五千蚊，佢就三日都冇回覆，過多一個月再打電話俾佢，佢冇聽，咁我就明白啦 ─ 你跌落谷底，仲借錢俾你咪即係掉落海，所以登天難，求人更難。」話雖如此，阿Paul身邊還有一個雪中送炭的朋友，他就是以前的拍檔「肥施」施介強。<br />\n<br />\n肥施現職港台監製，與Paul雖未有時常見面，但會久不久就打電話問候，「佢(Paul)有咩戲我都會追睇，佢之前都有好多不幸事，我都會打電話比佢，之前真係俾佢嚇親，個個都問我佢係唔係走咗，我即刻打畀佢，好彩佢有聽咋哈哈。」二人雖好久不見，但一拍即合，默契仍在，拍攝時配合得天衣無縫。肥施坦言相比起阿Paul，自己比較幸運，「或者個天知我承受到幾多苦難就俾幾多我，佢承受咁多，將來會有回報」。"},{"pid":"474f800bee556512281e71723b59198d6c7aa8c5","tid":84217,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:20:40.000Z","msg":"今時今日的阿Paul在博愛醫院董事局做全職雜務的工作。有時候要穿晚禮服做接待員，有時候要做解款員監護善款，有時候要走遍全香港九龍新界離島送貨，「你可以叫我車總理，乜嘢都要理，哈哈」。<br />\n<br />\n雖然樂觀積極的阿Paul已經面對現實，沒有再留戀以前風光的日子，但仍然喜歡演戲。「做演員，就好似食毒品，拍戲嗰時就似上電，我哋已經上咗癮啦。不過回頭一睇，今日有收入，聽日又唔知咩境況啦，我寧願繼續做我嘅工作。」談到夢想，阿Paul笑謂「冇咩夢想啦，夢想就係希望送一粒鑽石俾老婆，呢個承諾我經已講咗廿多年啦，俾膽石又話唔要哈哈。」"},{"pid":"761d58c68ccf1bba6bd558cfd175f1a8d0ebd883","tid":84217,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:23:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170116/280pix/1484541379_19c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170116%2F280pix%2F1484541379_19c3.jpg&h=d3ec26df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n車保羅曾憑住獨特外型，成為無數電影電視中的金牌綠葉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170116/280pix/1484541381_839c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170116%2F280pix%2F1484541381_839c.jpg&h=014ed726&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n03年約滿無綫後，阿Paul又失業，孫女又遇上交通意外，陷入人生低潮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170116/280pix/1484541384_e5e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170116%2F280pix%2F1484541384_e5e2.jpg&h=afbfc56b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正因為這段落魄的日子，令阿Paul感受到人情冷暖，見識到「登天難，求人更難」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170116/280pix/1484541386_78c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170116%2F280pix%2F1484541386_78c6.jpg&h=ed9fe805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幸好Paul身邊還有個會雪中送炭的朋友，他就是肥施<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170116/280pix/1484541387_fb0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170116%2F280pix%2F1484541387_fb0b.jpg&h=bdbca56a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當年Paul與肥施是最佳拍檔，常常一同演出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170116/280pix/1484541388_7eed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170116%2F280pix%2F1484541388_7eed.jpg&h=3f8a647c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖未有時常見面，但肥施久不久就打電話問候Paul"},{"pid":"83c6fd74770b3ad4aa18fd8a772f964fff936b37","tid":84217,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:26:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170116/280pix/1484541389_b5e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170116%2F280pix%2F1484541389_b5e2.jpg&h=c1a8b096&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿Paul已在博愛醫院董事局做了十年全職工作<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170116/280pix/1484541393_fb3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170116%2F280pix%2F1484541393_fb3f.jpg&h=5dcd1cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有時候要穿晚禮服做接待員，也要做解款員監護善款，亦要走遍全香港九龍新界離島送貨"},{"pid":"6b04d7f854c6a9b54ad89e3296fb8e1749af3b15","tid":84217,"uid":3936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:26:42.000Z","msg":"好記得佢拍過ETV<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527b770587e2c2a0908c84d491a15ffbd7060f01","tid":84217,"uid":3936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:26:53.000Z","msg":"好記得佢拍過ETV<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623010c63744e315ca5e11b25e5abdad95241770","tid":84217,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:27:06.000Z","msg":"60,70,80年代黃金時期都可撈到咁霉"},{"pid":"89173554a9cb6fc123857200bbd4e99a32cce9f3","tid":84217,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:29:05.000Z","msg":"好卡通個樣"},{"pid":"731ea38a8438f6d923feac79df9e2db90d5ffdf3","tid":84217,"uid":48222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:04:24.000Z","msg":"佢唔係有拍特務戇j咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18dd9e09d0f4c93c970ec46bd0343563d1ddc8e3","tid":84217,"uid":27359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:06:05.000Z","msg":"日日返工見到佢都係著個套迷彩衫+戰鬥背心"},{"pid":"8a9bbd2e63f96b82cfdc67fc7b9854cad3d5d5dd","tid":84217,"uid":55964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T16:09:59.000Z","msg":"每次睇到呢d新聞都會個鼻酸酸地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d867b965ffd703273